Class Road

  • java.lang.Object
    • es.ucm.fdi.model.SimulatedObject

    DirtRoad, LanesRoad

    public class Road
extends SimulatedObject
    Author:
    Pablo and Diego Class of the object road, extension of the SimulatedObject. this class represent the road which are traverse by vehicles, it goes from one junctions to other.

            Junction source,

        Constructor of the class. Calls the constructor of SimulatedObject with the id introduced as parameter, and assigns the other four parameters to the class attributes.
        Parameters:
        id - unique identifier of the road.
        lenght - the kilometers of the road.
        maxSpeed - maximum speed allowed in the road.
        source - junction which is the origin of the road.
        destination - junction which is the destination of the road.
